00:00:57.910 --> 00:00:59.690
Tonight's event
also marks something

00:00:59.690 --> 00:01:03.880
of a critical event in a
much longer drama, namely

00:01:03.880 --> 00:01:06.240
a set of events and
programs for the discussion

00:01:06.240 --> 00:01:08.310
of vital Native
American and indigenous

00:01:08.310 --> 00:01:13.940
issues, a theme running through
the 2015-2016 academic year

00:01:13.940 --> 00:01:17.840
here at Radcliffe, and a
theme chosen in partnership

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:20.670
with HUNAP entitled "The
Performance of Native

00:01:20.670 --> 00:01:23.260
and Indigenous Politics."

00:01:23.260 --> 00:01:26.880
Radcliffe has embarked upon
this series of conversations

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:29.690
and events not because
the Institute has

00:01:29.690 --> 00:01:32.360
particular expertise
in this area,

00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:36.650
but because Radcliffe and
Harvard have clear needs,

00:01:36.650 --> 00:01:40.210
and indeed, obligations
to enrich our dialogue

00:01:40.210 --> 00:01:43.060
on native and indigenous issues.

00:01:43.060 --> 00:01:47.240
A university is a conversation,
a highly bureaucratized

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:52.260
conversation to be sure, but
a vital dialogue nonetheless.

00:01:52.260 --> 00:01:54.620
And it is vital to
the future of Harvard

00:01:54.620 --> 00:01:58.480
and in deep consistency
with Harvard's native past

00:01:58.480 --> 00:02:01.450
that the voice of Native
American and indigenous peoples

00:02:01.450 --> 00:02:05.080
here be amplified
and strengthened.

00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:08.940
I hope tonight's event can
play a part, even a small part,

00:02:08.940 --> 00:02:12.570
in that strengthening,
in that amplification.

00:02:12.570 --> 00:02:15.640
And it is with thanks
to HUNAP and associated

00:02:15.640 --> 00:02:18.560
native and native studies
leaders at Harvard

00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:21.250
that this process
has been renewing.

00:02:21.250 --> 00:02:24.330
We at Radcliffe are
pleased and honored to play

00:02:24.330 --> 00:02:27.490
a small collaborative part in
this much larger and longer

00:02:27.490 --> 00:02:29.710
term dialogue.

