00:05:19.870 --> 00:05:21.980
As I was preparing
for tonight's remarks,

00:05:21.980 --> 00:05:24.010
I was struck by some
words in an article

00:05:24.010 --> 00:05:25.890
about the young
Sicangu Lakota artist,

00:05:25.890 --> 00:05:27.700
Frank Waln who
will be joining us

00:05:27.700 --> 00:05:29.920
in April at one of our events.

00:05:29.920 --> 00:05:31.690
The writer of the
article states,

00:05:31.690 --> 00:05:34.010
"We are born into stories.

00:05:34.010 --> 00:05:35.400
All of us.

00:05:35.400 --> 00:05:38.550
We must learn to address
the sins of the past

00:05:38.550 --> 00:05:40.130
so that we can
break and transcend

00:05:40.130 --> 00:05:42.780
those cycles of
trauma and abuse.

00:05:42.780 --> 00:05:44.690
These are the sorts
of messages we find

00:05:44.690 --> 00:05:47.620
in art worth talking about.

00:05:47.620 --> 00:05:49.380
As native and
indigenous people, we

00:05:49.380 --> 00:05:52.190
are each born into specific
and very purposeful

00:05:52.190 --> 00:05:53.860
creation stories.

00:05:53.860 --> 00:05:58.474
We embody these stories, and we
continue to live in them today.

00:05:58.474 --> 00:05:59.890
Many of us were
told these stories

00:05:59.890 --> 00:06:03.320
at a very young age in
order to educate us,

00:06:03.320 --> 00:06:06.400
or to teach us how to behave
in certain situations,

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:09.510
or to explain to us the natural
and the spiritual world that we

00:06:09.510 --> 00:06:10.770
live in."

00:06:10.770 --> 00:06:14.040
It seems quite often, though,
some stories were reiterated

00:06:14.040 --> 00:06:16.140
to us by older
brothers and sisters,

00:06:16.140 --> 00:06:20.640
or by aunties and uncles,
in order to scare us.

00:06:20.640 --> 00:06:24.690
Naturally, many of our stories
are about negative entities

00:06:24.690 --> 00:06:27.920
that often prey on our
people, particularly

00:06:27.920 --> 00:06:30.160
our women and our children.

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:33.160
These bad entities
can take many forms.

00:06:33.160 --> 00:06:34.980
They can be earthly beings.

00:06:34.980 --> 00:06:37.080
They can be animal beings.

00:06:37.080 --> 00:06:38.940
They can be spiritual
beings, and they

00:06:38.940 --> 00:06:41.210
can be other human beings.

00:06:41.210 --> 00:06:43.340
These beings can wreck
havoc on our people

00:06:43.340 --> 00:06:46.196
in violent and deadly waste.

00:06:46.196 --> 00:06:48.570
What our teasing family members
often neglect to tell us,

00:06:48.570 --> 00:06:51.260
however, is that our
stories almost always

00:06:51.260 --> 00:06:54.680
end with a defeat of
these negative entities.

00:06:54.680 --> 00:06:59.200
Our stories give us solutions
and ways to defend ourselves.

00:06:59.200 --> 00:07:01.820
They explain challenges
we must overcome in order

00:07:01.820 --> 00:07:05.670
to acquire specific
weapons or behaviors needed

00:07:05.670 --> 00:07:10.840
to defend the young, the
old, our women, and our men

00:07:10.840 --> 00:07:13.740
from beings that
threaten or hurt us.

00:07:13.740 --> 00:07:17.340
Our stories assure us that
we can be safe, healthy,

00:07:17.340 --> 00:07:19.864
and strong communities.

00:07:19.864 --> 00:07:21.780
Tonight, we are going
to hear a new creation .

00:07:21.780 --> 00:07:25.930
Story the story is about a
threat to our communities.

00:07:25.930 --> 00:07:29.810
It is about finding a way to
defend our women and children.

00:07:29.810 --> 00:07:33.290
This story's being told to
us tonight to encourage us

00:07:33.290 --> 00:07:37.530
and to remind us we can
overcome challenges.

00:07:37.530 --> 00:07:42.070
Tonight's story, however,
doesn't have a complete ending.

00:07:42.070 --> 00:07:43.620
In this story, we
are only beginning

00:07:43.620 --> 00:07:47.340
to understand and gather
legal weapons needed

00:07:47.340 --> 00:07:49.580
to defend our women.

00:07:49.580 --> 00:07:51.700
Tonight's story
provides only a sliver

00:07:51.700 --> 00:07:56.320
of the solution needed
to protect our futures.

00:07:56.320 --> 00:08:01.050
Still, the message of tonight's
story are worth talking about.

00:08:01.050 --> 00:08:03.330
Because the more
we tell this story,

00:08:03.330 --> 00:08:06.460
the closer we'll come to
achieving a full moon instead

00:08:06.460 --> 00:08:09.140
of a sliver of a full moon.

