and that it

00:13:41.355 --> 00:13:45.830
is important to love oneself,
to expect fairness and equality

00:13:45.830 --> 00:13:48.460
in any relationship.

00:13:48.460 --> 00:13:50.470
We pray that Sliver
of a Full Moon

00:13:50.470 --> 00:13:54.680
brings everybody
together with strength

00:13:54.680 --> 00:13:56.740
to break the silence
of domestic violence.

00:14:02.830 --> 00:14:06.860
-Thank you, Sachem Hendricks.

00:14:06.860 --> 00:14:09.090
