02:16:14.400 --> 02:16:15.410
system.

02:16:15.410 --> 02:16:17.900
And so things we want
to do outside of that,

02:16:17.900 --> 02:16:19.500
we have to get creative.

02:16:19.500 --> 02:16:22.660
-I think just this one follow up
