02:17:37.770 --> 02:17:41.080
do for indigenous women
who live in urban areas

02:17:41.080 --> 02:17:44.389
to fight all of the
abuse that we suffer.

02:17:44.389 --> 02:17:46.250
Because yes, we
need to address what

02:17:46.250 --> 02:17:48.719
happens on reservations,
and reserves in Canada,

02:17:48.719 --> 02:17:49.420
and so forth.

02:17:49.420 --> 02:17:52.870
But so many of us are urban,
and we're still experiencing

02:17:52.870 --> 02:17:54.250
a great deal of violence.

02:17:54.250 --> 02:17:56.520
And yes, technically,
the law is supposed

02:17:56.520 --> 02:17:58.120
to be there to protect us.

02:17:58.120 --> 02:17:59.670
But it certainly doesn't.

02:17:59.670 --> 02:18:03.959
So what are your legislative
or policy ideas on that?

02:18:07.870 --> 02:18:09.730
-I think criminal
justice systems

02:18:09.730 --> 02:18:11.370
need to be reformed generally.

02:18:11.370 --> 02:18:15.090
I think we've seen disparities
in enforcement and means

02:18:15.090 --> 02:18:18.420
of enforcement across
communities quite recently

02:18:18.420 --> 02:18:21.030
in very intense ways.

02:18:21.030 --> 02:18:23.620
And so I think that
our discussions

02:18:23.620 --> 02:18:26.620
about criminal justice should
incorporate Native women,

02:18:26.620 --> 02:18:28.260
they should
incorporate Native men.

02:18:28.260 --> 02:18:32.180
Because the statistics
are equally as troubling

02:18:32.180 --> 02:18:34.450
across minorities.

02:18:34.450 --> 02:18:36.969
And so that's one solution.

02:18:36.969 --> 02:18:39.690
But I think in
addition to that, there

02:18:39.690 --> 02:18:46.290
could be a culturally specific
legislative solutions that

02:18:46.290 --> 02:18:49.180
do look at the
particular problems

02:18:49.180 --> 02:18:51.490
the Native women face
within urban centers,

02:18:51.490 --> 02:18:54.129
and the fact that they're
taking with them this concern

02:18:54.129 --> 02:18:58.040
about government involvement
to those urban centers in a way

02:18:58.040 --> 02:19:02.400
to address that concern and the
way police interact with them

02:19:02.400 --> 02:19:04.219
in particular.

02:19:04.219 --> 02:19:06.330
-And this might sound
really abstract ,

02:19:06.330 --> 02:19:09.930
