rates of domestic violence

02:19:56.720 --> 02:19:59.170
against our native
women in urban areas,

02:19:59.170 --> 02:20:03.530
I think at the root of
that is the legal framework

02:20:03.530 --> 02:20:05.220
and the cultural
misunderstanding that

02:20:05.220 --> 02:20:07.390
perpetuates from that.

02:20:07.390 --> 02:20:10.290
When our tribal sovereign
nations aren't real,

02:20:10.290 --> 02:20:12.590
then how can how can any
American citizen conceive

02:20:12.590 --> 02:20:14.090
of their women as real?

02:20:14.090 --> 02:20:17.040
And I think that's the
problem we're facing.

